217;s been said. The best you can do is use more colorful and compelling la=
nguage on top of the existing points, and structure everything in a way tha=
t makes your team look good.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size=
: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">It should be fairly easy &#8=
211; there are no new points to make &#8211; but in the hands of a weak or =
